{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_03.gif?t=1739286303\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/steam_Embark_on_an_epic_campaign_Center.png?t=1739286303\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stand against the undead hordes in a campaign inspired by fantasy classics. Discover the continent of Aganor across many challenging missions, push back the darkness, and protect your people.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/steam_Protect_your_people_Center.png?t=1739286303\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the day to gather resources, fortify your town, and explore the surrounding lands. When the night falls, defend your people and their homes against the waves of enemies, until the break of dawn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_01.gif?t=1739286303\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/steam_Choose_your_heroes_Center.png?t=1739286303\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face the challenges with the help of legendary heroes - wizards, warriors, and more. Utilize their varied skills, level them up, and arm them with powerful artifacts won throughout your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_02.gif?t=1739286303\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/steam_Use_a_powerful_scenario_editor_Center.png?t=1739286303\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your own scenarios, maps, quests, and even whole, scripted campaigns with an extensive in-game editor. Share your creations with other players and set your imagination free.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/steam_Conquer_the_night_in_survival_mode_Center.png?t=1739286303\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test yourself in a challenging survival mode, where every night brings new, growing terrors. Survive the onslaught, and rebuild every morning to face the undead hordes again. Fight until you win glory\u2026 or reprieve in death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/extras/Darfall_SteamStore_GIF_04.gif?t=1739286303\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739286303","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/page.bg.jpg?t=1739286303","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/53d4376be702534588a7fa5d4861d542b00a5454/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739286303","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1961600/53d4376be702534588a7fa5d4861d542b00a5454/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739286303","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2085150,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/